<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Oilam haqida</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Opam haqida</h1>
    <p>
        Mening opam mehribon va aqlli inson.
        Men opamni juda yaxshi ko‘raman.
    </p>

    <h1>Ayam haqida</h1>
    <p>
        Mening ayam juda g‘amxo‘r va mehribon.
        Ayam doim meni qo‘llab-quvvatlaydi.
    </p>

</body>
</html>
